    "name": "Astradaemon",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Believed to be creations of the Four Horsemen, astradaemons live out their existence in search of souls to harvest. These deadly creatures are ravening planar predators, openly hunting throughout the void for souls on which to feed. These voracious creatures are the personifications of death resulting from negative energy or level drain. Their vile touch drains life force from their enemies, and even perishing near them sates their thirst for life and souls."
        }
    ],
